 《惊声尖叫 7》将引进西德尼女儿的新一代演员阵容https://www.nme.com/news/film/scream-7-to-introduce-new- Generation-with-sidneys-daughter-cast-3815173?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=scream-7-to-introduce-新一代与悉尼女儿演员阵容Damian JonesFri, 22 Nov 2024 17:55:16 +0000 Film NewsNewsHorror https://www.nme.com/?p=3815173 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024_isabelmay_getty_2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="伊莎贝尔·梅" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024_isabelmay_getty_2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024_isabelmay_getty_2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024_isabelmay_getty_2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024_isabelmay_getty_2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024_isabelmay_getty_2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024_isabelmay_getty_2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>续集最近确定将于 2026 年上映</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/scream-7-to-introduce-new-generation-with-sidneys-daughter-cast-3815173">介绍西德尼女儿演员阵容的新一代《惊声尖叫 7》的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024_isabelmay_getty_2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="伊莎贝尔·梅" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024_isabelmay_getty_2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024_isabelmay_getty_2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024_isabelmay_getty_2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024_isabelmay_getty_2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024_isabelmay_getty_2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024_isabelmay_getty_2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>伊莎贝尔·梅在<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/scream"><em>《惊声尖叫7》</em></a>中饰演西德尼·普雷斯科特（内芙·坎贝尔饰）的女儿。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/heres-when-scream-7-is-coming-out-3798843">《惊声尖叫 7》即将上映</a></strong></li></ul><p>据<a href="https://ew.com/scream-7-sidney-daughter-isabel-may-cast-neve-campbell-8749244" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《娱乐周刊》</em></a>报道，这位<a href="https://www.nme.com/series/yellowstone"><em>《黄石公园》</em></a>的衍生明星已经加入了即将上映的<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/horror">恐怖</a>电影的演员阵容，坎贝尔将回归担任主演。</p><p>梅因扮演埃尔莎·达顿 (Elsa Dutton) 而闻名，她<em>是 1883 年</em>和<em>1923 年</em>两部<em>黄石公园</em>前传<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/paramount">派拉蒙+</a>系列剧中的主角和旁白。她最近还出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/apple-tv">Apple TV+</a>系列节目<a href="https://www.nme.com/series/masters-of-the-air"><em>《空中大师》</em></a>中。</p><p>此前，帕特里克·德姆西最近也证实“有一次关于他回归扮演马克·金凯德的对话”，马克·金凯德是电影最新时间线中西德尼的丈夫。他最后一次扮演这个角色是在2000年的<em>《惊声尖叫3》中。</em></p><p> “我正在等待剧本，”演员说。 “我还没有看到任何东西，所以我们会看看会发生什么。”</p><p>续集<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/heres-when-scream-7-is-coming-out-3798843">最近确定将于 2026 年 2 月 27 日上映</a>。这部即将上映的电影将由该系列的创始人凯文·威廉姆森执导。 </p><figure style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/ghostface-could-be-coming-to-mortal-kombat-1.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" /><figcaption class="wp-caption-text"> 《惊声尖叫 6》来源：派拉蒙影业</figcaption></figure><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/melissa-barrera">梅丽莎·巴雷拉 (Melissa Barrera)</a>曾领导<em>《惊声尖叫 5》</em>和《惊声尖叫<em>6》</em> ，但<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/fans-vow-to-boycott-scream-vii-after-melissa-barrera-is-dropped-over-israel-hamas-war-post-3546483">去年被<em>《惊声尖叫 7》</em>解雇<i></i></a>在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/fans-vow-to-boycott-scream-vii-after-melissa-barrera-is-dropped-over-israel-hamas-war-post-3546483">Instagram 上发帖支持巴勒斯坦</a>后。  联合负责人<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jenna-ortega">珍娜·奥尔特加 (Jenna Ortega)</a>也<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/jenna-ortega-will-not-be-returning-to-the-scream-franchise-3546990">宣布，由于其他日程安排，她不会返回</a>。</p><p>当时，坎贝尔曾出演过前五部<em>《惊声尖叫》</em>电影，但由于“片酬差异”错过了去年的<em>《惊声尖叫 6》，</em>因此与该系列保持了距离。</p><p>巴雷拉被解雇后， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/neve-campbell-returns-scream-melissa-barrera-sacking-3600529">坎贝尔再次获得主演角色，并</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/neve-campbell-says-she-was-sad-to-miss-last-scream-film-as-she-opens-up-about-return-3761903">在“当我谈论薪酬差异以及当我谈论[<em>尖叫6</em>谈判]不感到尊重时工作室听到了我的意见”后同意回归。</a></p><p>九月下旬，考特尼·考克斯（Courtney Cox）——该系列电影中唯一一位出现在所有六部已上映电影中的演员——<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/courteney-cox-not-officially-signed-on-for-scream-7-3796423">证实她还没有正式签约出演第七部电影</a>：“他们一直在重写。我又不是不知道发生了什么事。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/scream-7-to-introduce-new-generation-with-sidneys-daughter-cast-3815173">介绍西德尼女儿演员阵容的新一代《惊声尖叫 7》的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
